==Ôtenawa Âpihtâkosisânak==
Âpihtâkosisânak ayâwak ayinânew ôtenawa  ochi Alberta; Mostos-Sâkahikan, Mekiwin-Sâkahikan (Utikuma), Pimiskâkan-Maskotew, Sâkâstenohk-Maskotew, Kichi-Maskotew, Kikino, Elizabeth, ekwa Kinosewesâhahikan.  Nema askiy 1.28 mâwaci-kihci-mitâtahtomitanaw ‘acres’.

